flowchart LR
  %% Semantic search architecture
  Q[User query] --> Q1[Embedding model\nall-MiniLM-L6-v2]
  Q1 --> V[Query vector]
  D[Course corpus\ndata/*.csv] --> I[Indexer\nscripts/embed.py]
  I --> E[Course embeddings]
  I --> P[2D projections\nPCA UMAP TSNE]
  E --> S[Course store\nPostgreSQL float arrays]
  P --> S
  S --> R[Search and ranking\ncosine or pgvector]
  V --> R
  R --> M[Top matches]
  V --> X[Projection with query point]
  S --> X
  M --> O[Semantic search output]
  X --> O
